## LTP configuration for Node A
## Engine ID: 1
## Remote engine: 2 (Node B)
##
## LTP sends segments via UDP to local modem at :1113
## LTP receives segments via UDP from local modem at :1114

1 32

## span to engine 2 (Node B):
##   max segment size: 1400 bytes
##   aggregation size limit: 1 block
##   aggregation time limit: 1 sec
##   outbound LSO: udplso sends to local modem TX input on 127.0.0.1:1113
a span 2 32 1400 1 1 'udplso 127.0.0.1:1113'

## inbound LSI: udplsi listens for datagrams from local modem RX output on :1114
s 'udplsi 127.0.0.1:1114'
